{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Code Me, dsewnr","author":"dsewnr"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c75c1595-d4c4-542b-993f-8d5f6013cd94","excerpt":"坐了兩個多月租屋處附的燒屁股椅子… 終於等到這一天了… 因為在家用電腦的時間也算是蠻長的，而且平常客廳也不太會開冷氣，所以起了一個要買網椅的念頭！ 某大大是一直推什麼 Herman Miller 啦… 但小弟的財力無法負荷那麼狂暴的攻擊，會直接倒地 Orz…","html":"<p>坐了兩個多月租屋處附的燒屁股椅子… 終於等到這一天了…</p>\n<!--more-->\n<p>因為在家用電腦的時間也算是蠻長的，而且平常客廳也不太會開冷氣，所以起了一個要買網椅的念頭！</p>\n<p>某大大是一直推什麼 Herman Miller 啦… 但小弟的財力無法負荷那麼狂暴的攻擊，會直接倒地 Orz</p>\n<p>於是到處做功課花了蠻長一段時間的，在今天下訂一個月的 Enjoy 121 終於來了！！！</p>\n<h3>直接裝箱寄到府，不用自己組！</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d747f68424d777be62d313c089df0e04/0eb7a/enjoy-121-0.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 194.52887537993922%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"enjoy 121 0\"\n        title=\"enjoy 121 0\"\n        src=\"/static/d747f68424d777be62d313c089df0e04/55071/enjoy-121-0.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d747f68424d777be62d313c089df0e04/493b1/enjoy-121-0.jpg 163w,\n/static/d747f68424d777be62d313c089df0e04/17f95/enjoy-121-0.jpg 325w,\n/static/d747f68424d777be62d313c089df0e04/55071/enjoy-121-0.jpg 650w,\n/static/d747f68424d777be62d313c089df0e04/0eb7a/enjoy-121-0.jpg 658w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>開箱！</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/eaa331d735feecd6cba987b0e9aaf958/30b67/enjoy-121-1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.47236704900936%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"enjoy 121 1\"\n        title=\"enjoy 121 1\"\n        src=\"/static/eaa331d735feecd6cba987b0e9aaf958/55071/enjoy-121-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/eaa331d735feecd6cba987b0e9aaf958/493b1/enjoy-121-1.jpg 163w,\n/static/eaa331d735feecd6cba987b0e9aaf958/17f95/enjoy-121-1.jpg 325w,\n/static/eaa331d735feecd6cba987b0e9aaf958/55071/enjoy-121-1.jpg 650w,\n/static/eaa331d735feecd6cba987b0e9aaf958/30b67/enjoy-121-1.jpg 959w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>被搶先體驗了 XD</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/754b6fbbcdf9bd96de2b8d29e91ced72/30b67/enjoy-121-2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.47236704900936%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"enjoy 121 2\"\n        title=\"enjoy 121 2\"\n        src=\"/static/754b6fbbcdf9bd96de2b8d29e91ced72/55071/enjoy-121-2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/754b6fbbcdf9bd96de2b8d29e91ced72/493b1/enjoy-121-2.jpg 163w,\n/static/754b6fbbcdf9bd96de2b8d29e91ced72/17f95/enjoy-121-2.jpg 325w,\n/static/754b6fbbcdf9bd96de2b8d29e91ced72/55071/enjoy-121-2.jpg 650w,\n/static/754b6fbbcdf9bd96de2b8d29e91ced72/30b67/enjoy-121-2.jpg 959w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3>安靜的輪子</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/97bd7ea05af48cc8f34b90ffe7b73413/7b0d7/enjoy-121-3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.921875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"enjoy 121 3\"\n        title=\"enjoy 121 3\"\n        src=\"/static/97bd7ea05af48cc8f34b90ffe7b73413/55071/enjoy-121-3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/97bd7ea05af48cc8f34b90ffe7b73413/493b1/enjoy-121-3.jpg 163w,\n/static/97bd7ea05af48cc8f34b90ffe7b73413/17f95/enjoy-121-3.jpg 325w,\n/static/97bd7ea05af48cc8f34b90ffe7b73413/55071/enjoy-121-3.jpg 650w,\n/static/97bd7ea05af48cc8f34b90ffe7b73413/4194c/enjoy-121-3.jpg 975w,\n/static/97bd7ea05af48cc8f34b90ffe7b73413/7b0d7/enjoy-121-3.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>比原本的椅子好坐多了，輪子滑起來蠻安靜的，現在正坐著這張椅子吹電扇，屁屁好涼好舒服 XD</p>\n<p>[2019/10/24 Updated] 坐了一個多月真的很好坐，完全沒後悔，女兒超愛跟我搶椅子！</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Ergohuman Enjoy 121 企業版開箱，新椅子來囉~","date":"September 11, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/enjoy-121/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/upgrade-mongodb-from-3.2-to-4.2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Upgrade MongoDB From 3.2 to 4.2"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/datacon-2019/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"DataCon.TW 2019"}}}}